    A[Current vault is bound] --> B[User initiates rebind]
    B --> C[New binding TX created]
    C --> D[Old wallet signs TXID]
    D --> E{Valid signature?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Update vault.txid]
    F --> G[Recompute vault_id]
